```
Article 2 (Mission):
	The purposes and missions of this esteemed organization shall be as follows:
    Mission 1: The encouragement and pursuit of various forms of literature at
        behest of the current sitting Principle Sibling (See Article 4).
    Mission 2: The expansion and development of the ‘cultural eye.’
        I.E. a truer understanding of those powerful, abstract ideas that are the makeup and fabric of our modern world.
    Mission 3: The cultivation of an independent and confident mind.
    Mission 4: Family time.
```